    "body": "Stumbled across the following CMake bug:\r\n\r\nhttps://cmake.org/Bug/bug_relationship_graph.php?bug_id=15386&graph=relation\r\n\r\nCMake Versions 3.1.2 and newer build fine with openssl 1.0.2, whereas older releases fail. I could reproduce the problem when trying to install CMake 2.8.10.2, which is listed as \"safe version\"\r\n\r\nIn the CMake bug report, the following patch is attached:\r\n\r\nhttps://cmake.org/gitweb?p=cmake.git;a=commitdiff;h=c5d9a8283cfac15b4a5a07f18d5eb10c1f388505",
